62 // ******************************************************************************************
63 EndEffectorsWidget::EndEffectorsWidget(QWidget* parent, const MoveItConfigDataPtr& config_data)
64  : SetupScreenWidget(parent), config_data_(config_data)
65 {
66  // Basic widget container
67  QVBoxLayout* layout = new QVBoxLayout();
68 
69  // Top Header Area ------------------------------------------------
70 
71  HeaderWidget* header = new HeaderWidget("Define End Effectors",
72  "Setup your robot's end effectors. These are planning groups "
73  "corresponding to grippers or tools, attached to a parent "
74  "planning group (an arm). The specified parent link is used as the "
75  "reference frame for IK attempts.",
76  this);
77  layout->addWidget(header);
78 
79  // Create contents screens ---------------------------------------
80 
81  effector_list_widget_ = createContentsWidget();
82  effector_edit_widget_ = createEditWidget();
83 
84  // Create stacked layout -----------------------------------------
85  stacked_widget_ = new QStackedWidget(this);
86  stacked_widget_->addWidget(effector_list_widget_); // screen index 0
87  stacked_widget_->addWidget(effector_edit_widget_); // screen index 1
88  layout->addWidget(stacked_widget_);
89 
90  // Finish Layout --------------------------------------------------
91  this->setLayout(layout);
92 }

97 QWidget* EndEffectorsWidget::createContentsWidget()
98 {
99  // Main widget
100  QWidget* content_widget = new QWidget(this);
101

104 
105  // Table ------------ ------------------------------------------------

110  data_table_->setSelectionBehavior(QAbstractItemView::SelectRows);
111  connect(data_table_, SIGNAL(cellDoubleClicked(int, int)), this, SLOT(editDoubleClicked(int, int)));

113  layout->addWidget(data_table_);
114 
115  // Set header labels
116  QStringList header_list;
117  header_list.append("End Effector Name");
118  header_list.append("Group Name");
119  header_list.append("Parent Link");
120  header_list.append("Parent Group");
121  data_table_->setHorizontalHeaderLabels(header_list);
122 
123  // Bottom Buttons --------------------------------------------------
124 
125  QHBoxLayout* controls_layout = new QHBoxLayout();
126 
127  // Spacer
128  controls_layout->addItem(new QSpacerItem(20, 20, QSizePolicy::Expanding, QSizePolicy::Minimum));
129 
130  // Edit Selected Button
131  btn_edit_ = new QPushButton("&Edit Selected", this);
132  btn_edit_->setSizePolicy(QSizePolicy::Expanding, QSizePolicy::Preferred);
133  btn_edit_->setMaximumWidth(300);
134  btn_edit_->hide(); // show once we know if there are existing poses
135  connect(btn_edit_, SIGNAL(clicked()), this, SLOT(editSelected()));

138

142  controls_layout->addWidget(btn_delete_);
143  controls_layout->setAlignment(btn_delete_, Qt::AlignRight);
144 
145  // Add end effector Button

147  btn_add->setSizePolicy(QSizePolicy::Expanding, QSizePolicy::Preferred);
148  btn_add->setMaximumWidth(300);
149  connect(btn_add, SIGNAL(clicked()), this, SLOT(showNewScreen()));
150  controls_layout->addWidget(btn_add);

153  // Add layout

165 QWidget* EndEffectorsWidget::createEditWidget()
166 {
167  // Main widget
168  QWidget* edit_widget = new QWidget(this);
169  // Layout
170  QVBoxLayout* layout = new QVBoxLayout();
171 
172  // Simple form -------------------------------------------

176

183  group_name_field_->setEditable(false);
184  form_layout->addRow("End Effector Group:", group_name_field_);

186  SLOT(previewClickedString(const QString&)));
187 
188  // Parent Link input
189  parent_name_field_ = new QComboBox(this);
190  parent_name_field_->setEditable(false);
191  form_layout->addRow("Parent Link (usually part of the arm):", parent_name_field_);
192 
193  // Parent Group input
194  parent_group_name_field_ = new QComboBox(this);
195  parent_group_name_field_->setEditable(false);
196  form_layout->addRow("Parent Group (optional):", parent_group_name_field_);

198  layout->addLayout(form_layout);
199 
200  // Bottom Buttons --------------------------------------------------
201 
202  QHBoxLayout* controls_layout = new QHBoxLayout();
203  controls_layout->setContentsMargins(0, 25, 0, 15);
204 
205  // Spacer

207 
208  // Save
209  btn_save_ = new QPushButton("&Save", this);
210  btn_save_->setMaximumWidth(200);
211  connect(btn_save_, SIGNAL(clicked()), this, SLOT(doneEditing()));
212  controls_layout->addWidget(btn_save_);
213  controls_layout->setAlignment(btn_save_, Qt::AlignRight);
214 
215  // Cancel
216  btn_cancel_ = new QPushButton("&Cancel", this);
217  btn_cancel_->setMaximumWidth(200);
218  connect(btn_cancel_, SIGNAL(clicked()), this, SLOT(cancelEditing()));
219  controls_layout->addWidget(btn_cancel_);
220  controls_layout->setAlignment(btn_cancel_, Qt::AlignRight);
221 
222  // Add layout
223  layout->addLayout(controls_layout);
224 
225  // Set layout -----------------------------------------------------
226  edit_widget->setLayout(layout);
227 
228  return edit_widget;
229 }

260 // ******************************************************************************************
261 // Preview whatever element is selected
262 // ******************************************************************************************
263 void EndEffectorsWidget::previewClicked(int /*row*/, int /*column*/)
264 {
265  // Get list of all selected items
266  QList<QTableWidgetItem*> selected = data_table_->selectedItems();
267 
268  // Check that an element was selected
269  if (selected.empty())
270  return;
271 
272  // Find the selected in datastructure
273  srdf::Model::EndEffector* effector = findEffectorByName(selected[0]->text().toStdString());
274 
275  // Unhighlight all links
276  Q_EMIT unhighlightAll();
277 
278  // Highlight group
279  Q_EMIT highlightGroup(effector->component_group_);
280 }

314 // ******************************************************************************************
315 // Edit effector
316 // ******************************************************************************************
317 void EndEffectorsWidget::edit(const std::string& name)
318 {
319  // Remember what we are editing
320  current_edit_effector_ = name;
321 
322  // Find the selected in datastruture
323  srdf::Model::EndEffector* effector = findEffectorByName(name);
324 
325  // Set effector name
326  effector_name_field_->setText(effector->name_.c_str());
327 
328  // Set effector parent link
329  int index = parent_name_field_->findText(effector->parent_link_.c_str());
330  if (index == -1)
331  {
332  QMessageBox::critical(this, "Error Loading", "Unable to find parent link in drop down box");
333  return;
334  }
335  parent_name_field_->setCurrentIndex(index);
336 
337  // Set group:
338  index = group_name_field_->findText(effector->component_group_.c_str());
339  if (index == -1)
340  {
341  QMessageBox::critical(this, "Error Loading", "Unable to find group name in drop down box");
342  return;
343  }
344  group_name_field_->setCurrentIndex(index);
345 
346  // Set parent group:
347  index = parent_group_name_field_->findText(effector->parent_group_.c_str());
348  if (index == -1)
349  {
350  QMessageBox::critical(this, "Error Loading", "Unable to find parent group name in drop down box");
351  return;
352  }
353  parent_group_name_field_->setCurrentIndex(index);
354 
355  // Switch to screen
356  stacked_widget_->setCurrentIndex(1);
357 
358  // Announce that this widget is in modal mode
359  Q_EMIT isModal(true);
360 }

362 // ******************************************************************************************
363 // Populate the combo dropdown box with avail group names
364 // ******************************************************************************************
365 void EndEffectorsWidget::loadGroupsComboBox()
366 {
367  // Remove all old groups
368  group_name_field_->clear();
369  parent_group_name_field_->clear();
370  parent_group_name_field_->addItem(""); // optional setting
371 
372  // Add all group names to combo box
373  for (srdf::Model::Group& group : config_data_->srdf_->groups_)
374  {
375  group_name_field_->addItem(group.name_.c_str());
376  parent_group_name_field_->addItem(group.name_.c_str());

380 // ******************************************************************************************
381 // Populate the combo dropdown box with avail parent links
382 // ******************************************************************************************
383 void EndEffectorsWidget::loadParentComboBox()
384 {
385  // Remove all old groups
386  parent_name_field_->clear();
387 
388  // Get all links in robot model
389  std::vector<const moveit::core::LinkModel*> link_models = config_data_->getRobotModel()->getLinkModels();
390 
391  // Add all links to combo box
392  for (std::vector<const moveit::core::LinkModel*>::const_iterator link_it = link_models.begin();
393  link_it < link_models.end(); ++link_it)
394  {
395  parent_name_field_->addItem((*link_it)->getName().c_str());
396  }
397 }

399 // ******************************************************************************************
400 // Find the associated data by name
401 // ******************************************************************************************
402 srdf::Model::EndEffector* EndEffectorsWidget::findEffectorByName(const std::string& name)
403 {
404  // Find the group state we are editing based on the effector name
405  srdf::Model::EndEffector* searched_group = nullptr; // used for holding our search results
406 
407  for (srdf::Model::EndEffector& end_effector : config_data_->srdf_->end_effectors_)
408  {
409  if (end_effector.name_ == name) // string match
410  {
411  searched_group = &end_effector; // convert to pointer from iterator
412  break; // we are done searching
413  }
414  }
415 
416  // Check if effector was found
417  if (searched_group == nullptr) // not found
418  {
419  QMessageBox::critical(this, "Error Saving", "An internal error has occured while saving. Quitting.");
420  QApplication::quit();
421  }
422 
423  return searched_group;
424 }

426 // ******************************************************************************************
427 // Delete currently editing item
428 // ******************************************************************************************
429 void EndEffectorsWidget::deleteSelected()
430 {
431  // Get list of all selected items
432  QList<QTableWidgetItem*> selected = data_table_->selectedItems();
433 
434  // Check that an element was selected
435  if (selected.empty())
436  return;
437 
438  // Get selected name and edit it
439  current_edit_effector_ = selected[0]->text().toStdString();
440 
441  // Confirm user wants to delete group
442  if (QMessageBox::question(this, "Confirm End Effector Deletion",
443  QString("Are you sure you want to delete the end effector '")
444  .append(current_edit_effector_.c_str())
445  .append("'?"),
446  QMessageBox::Ok | QMessageBox::Cancel) == QMessageBox::Cancel)
447  {
448  return;
449  }
450 
451  // Delete effector from vector
452  for (std::vector<srdf::Model::EndEffector>::iterator effector_it = config_data_->srdf_->end_effectors_.begin();
453  effector_it != config_data_->srdf_->end_effectors_.end(); ++effector_it)
454  {
455  // check if this is the group we want to delete
456  if (effector_it->name_ == current_edit_effector_) // string match
457  {
458  config_data_->srdf_->end_effectors_.erase(effector_it);
459  break;
460  }
461  }
462 
463  // Reload main screen table
464  loadDataTable();
465  config_data_->changes |= MoveItConfigData::END_EFFECTORS;
466 }

468 // ******************************************************************************************
469 // Save editing changes
470 // ******************************************************************************************
471 void EndEffectorsWidget::doneEditing()
472 {
473  // Get a reference to the supplied strings
474  const std::string effector_name = effector_name_field_->text().toStdString();
475 
476  // Used for editing existing groups
477  srdf::Model::EndEffector* searched_data = nullptr;
478 
479  // Check that name field is not empty
480  if (effector_name.empty())
481  {
482  QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error Saving", "A name must be specified for the end effector!");
483  return;
484  }
485 
486  // Check if this is an existing group
487  if (!current_edit_effector_.empty())
488  {
489  // Find the group we are editing based on the goup name string
490  searched_data = findEffectorByName(current_edit_effector_);
491  }
492 
493  // Check that the effector name is unique
494  for (const auto& eef : config_data_->srdf_->end_effectors_)
495  {
496  if (eef.name_ == effector_name)
497  {
498  // is this our existing effector? check if effector pointers are same
499  if (&eef != searched_data)
500  {
501  QMessageBox::warning(
502  this, "Error Saving",
503  QString("An end-effector named '").append(effector_name.c_str()).append("'already exists!"));
504  return;
505  }
506  }
507  }
508 
509  // Check that a group was selected
510  if (group_name_field_->currentText().isEmpty())
511  {
512  QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error Saving", "A group that contains the links of the end-effector must be chosen!");
513  return;
514  }
515 
516  // Check that a parent link was selected
517  if (parent_name_field_->currentText().isEmpty())
518  {
519  QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error Saving", "A parent link must be chosen!");
520  return;
521  }
522 
523  const moveit::core::JointModelGroup* jmg =
524  config_data_->getRobotModel()->getJointModelGroup(group_name_field_->currentText().toStdString());
525  /*
526  if (jmg->hasLinkModel(parent_name_field_->currentText().toStdString()))
527  {
528  QMessageBox::warning( this, "Error Saving", QString::fromStdString("Group " +
529  group_name_field_->currentText().toStdString() + " contains the link " +
530  parent_name_field_->currentText().toStdString() + ". However, the parent link of the end-effector should not belong to
531  the group for the end-effector itself."));
532  return;
533  }
534  */
535  if (!parent_group_name_field_->currentText().isEmpty())
536  {
537  jmg = config_data_->getRobotModel()->getJointModelGroup(parent_group_name_field_->currentText().toStdString());
538  if (!jmg->hasLinkModel(parent_name_field_->currentText().toStdString()))
539  {
540  QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error Saving",
541  QString::fromStdString("The specified parent group '" +
542  parent_group_name_field_->currentText().toStdString() +
543  "' must contain the specified parent link '" +
544  parent_name_field_->currentText().toStdString() + "'."));
545  return;
546  }
547  }
548 
549  config_data_->changes |= MoveItConfigData::END_EFFECTORS;
550 
551  // Save the new effector name or create the new effector ----------------------------
552  bool is_new = false;
553 
554  if (searched_data == nullptr) // create new
555  {
556  is_new = true;
557 
558  searched_data = new srdf::Model::EndEffector();
559  }
560 
561  // Copy name data ----------------------------------------------------
562  searched_data->name_ = effector_name;
563  searched_data->parent_link_ = parent_name_field_->currentText().toStdString();
564  searched_data->component_group_ = group_name_field_->currentText().toStdString();
565  searched_data->parent_group_ = parent_group_name_field_->currentText().toStdString();
566 
567  // Insert new effectors into group state vector --------------------------
568  if (is_new)
569  {
570  config_data_->srdf_->end_effectors_.push_back(*searched_data);
571  delete searched_data;
572  }
573 
574  // Finish up ------------------------------------------------------
575 
576  // Reload main screen table
577  loadDataTable();
578 
579  // Switch to screen
580  stacked_widget_->setCurrentIndex(0);
581 
582  // Announce that this widget is not in modal mode
583  Q_EMIT isModal(false);
584 }

601 // ******************************************************************************************
602 // Load the end effectors into the table
603 // ******************************************************************************************
604 void EndEffectorsWidget::loadDataTable()
605 {
606  // Disable Table
607  data_table_->setUpdatesEnabled(false); // prevent table from updating until we are completely done
608  data_table_->setDisabled(true); // make sure we disable it so that the cellChanged event is not called
609  data_table_->clearContents();
610 
611  // Set size of datatable
612  data_table_->setRowCount(config_data_->srdf_->end_effectors_.size());
613 
614  // Loop through every end effector
615  int row = 0;
616  for (const auto& eef : config_data_->srdf_->end_effectors_)
617  {
618  // Create row elements
619  QTableWidgetItem* data_name = new QTableWidgetItem(eef.name_.c_str());
620  data_name->setFlags(Qt::ItemIsEnabled | Qt::ItemIsSelectable);
621  QTableWidgetItem* group_name = new QTableWidgetItem(eef.component_group_.c_str());
622  group_name->setFlags(Qt::ItemIsEnabled | Qt::ItemIsSelectable);
623  QTableWidgetItem* parent_name = new QTableWidgetItem(eef.parent_link_.c_str());
624  group_name->setFlags(Qt::ItemIsEnabled | Qt::ItemIsSelectable);
625  QTableWidgetItem* parent_group_name = new QTableWidgetItem(eef.parent_group_.c_str());
626  parent_group_name->setFlags(Qt::ItemIsEnabled | Qt::ItemIsSelectable);
627 
628  // Add to table
629  data_table_->setItem(row, 0, data_name);
630  data_table_->setItem(row, 1, group_name);
631  data_table_->setItem(row, 2, parent_name);
632  data_table_->setItem(row, 3, parent_group_name);
633 
634  // Increment counter
635  ++row;
636  }
637 
638  // Reenable
639  data_table_->setUpdatesEnabled(true); // prevent table from updating until we are completely done
640  data_table_->setDisabled(false); // make sure we disable it so that the cellChanged event is not called
641 
642  // Resize header
643  data_table_->resizeColumnToContents(0);
644  data_table_->resizeColumnToContents(1);
645  data_table_->resizeColumnToContents(2);
646  data_table_->resizeColumnToContents(3);
647 
648  // Show edit button if applicable
649  if (!config_data_->srdf_->end_effectors_.empty())
650  btn_edit_->show();
651 }
